title: Dragons are on a roll as they roar to victory
text: PUBLISHED: October 15, 2015 7:59 am LAST UPDATED: October 15, 2015 4:01 pm Dragons are on a roll as they roar to victory Burntwood Dragons Knights Under-10s sent us in these pictures after their match against Streetly-based Colron Boys Under-10s. Burntwood Dragons line up, back row, from left: Coach Stuart Allen, manager Steve Parton, coach Ade Bladon. Middle: Jack Parton, Drew Seymour, Joshua Massey, Sebastien Black, Jamie Youll. Front: Kodi Jonesm Luke Bladon, Yaseen Abu Khalil, Harry Allen, James Rose.
